org.bonitasoft.engine.bpm.process

Class ProcessInstanceSearchDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bonitasoft.engine.bpm.process.ProcessInstanceSearchDescriptor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProcessInstanceSearchDescriptor

    public class ProcessInstanceSearchDescriptor
extends Object
    Search descriptors are used to filter / sort results of a generic search.
    ProcessInstanceSearchDescriptor defines the fields that can be used as filters or sort fields on List<ProcessInstance> returning methods.
    Since:
    6.0.0
    Author:
    Yanyan Liu, Elias Ricken de Medeiros, Matthieu Chaffotte, Emmanuel Duchastenier, Celine Souchet
    See Also:
    ProcessRuntimeAPI, ProcessInstance
